import "./App.css"; import { CurriculoService } from "./services/CurriculoService"; import { CepService } from "./services/CepService"; import React from "react"; const dataInit = { logradouro: "", bairro: "", cidade: "", uf: "", }; class App extends React.Component { constructor(props) { super(props); this.state = { data : dataInit }; } Enviar = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); const formData = new FormData(e.target); const data = Object.fromEntries(formData); CurriculoService.apiPost(data); }; async buscarCep() { const cep = document.querySelector(".cep1").value + document.querySelector(".cep2").value; if (cep.lenght < 8) { return; } await CepService.ConsultaCep(cep).then((result) => { if (result.data.hasOwnProperty("erro")) { alert("CEP não existente"); } else { console.log(result.data.uf) this.state.data.uf = result.data.uf; this.state.data.cidade = result.data.localidade; this.state.data.bairro = result.data.bairro; this.state.data.logradouro = result.data.logradouro; } }); } handleChange = (e) => { const value = e.target.value; const name = e.target.name; this.setState({ [name]: value }, () => { this.buscarCep(); }); }; render() { return (














































































); } } export default App;
